apollo_short_description:
Since 1995, Sara Brook and her Dessert Gallery crew have been serving up some of Houston's favorite sweet treats. 

We love making desserts that bring people together, help create sweet memories, and make the world a better place. Our specialties are:

- Chocolate chunk cookies dipped in chocolate;
- The world's best brownies (seriously!);
- Incredible whole cakes and gorgeous gift trays for special occasions;
- Cakes and sugar cookies customized with your photographs.

And so much more! Get in touch or stop by our store to find out what we can do for you.
